      98.53,
      293.94,
      124.89
    ],
    "text": "An Act to repeal the Presidents\u2019 Entitlements Act, No. 4 of 1986",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      141.42,
      308.51,
      166.29
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka as follows: -",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      181.17,
      308.52,
      208.6
    ],
    "text": "1. This Act may be cited as the Presidents\u2019 Entitlements (Repeal) Act, No. 18 of 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      222.57,
      308.5,
      263.8
    ],
    "text": "2. The Presidents\u2019 Entitlements Act, No. 4 of 1986 (hereinafter referred to as the \u201crepealed Act\u201d) is hereby repealed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      78.0,
      275.97,
      306.0,
      289.81
    ],
    "text": "3. For the avoidance of doubt, it is hereby declared that-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      302.93,
      308.51,
      354.49
    ],
    "text": "(a) any residence provided to, or monthly allowance paid to, a former President or the widow of a former President in terms of the provisions of section 2 of the repealed Act;",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      367.93,
      308.51,
      432.49
    ],
    "text": "(b) monthly secretarial allowance paid to, and official transport and such other facilities provided to, a former President or the widow of a former President in terms of the provisions of section 3 of the repealed Act; and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      445.93,
      308.5,
      485.4
    ],
    "text": "(c) monthly pension paid to the widow of a former President in terms of the provisions of section 4 of the repealed Act,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.0,
      499.22,
      308.51,
      538.09
    ],
    "text": "preceding the date of commencement of this Act, shall no longer be provided with or paid to, on and after the date of commencement of this Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      109.09,
      62.36,
      262.91,
      75.85
    ],
    "text": "[Certified on 10th of September, 2025]",
    "fonts": [
      "MinionPro-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      114.0,
      38.53,
      345.29,
      52.01
    ],
    "text": "2Presidents\u2019 Entitlements (Repeal) Act, No. 18 of 2025",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      114.0,
      74.37,
      356.51,
      100.09
    ],
